001package edu.cnm.deepdive.appstarter.model.dao;
002
003import androidx.lifecycle.LiveData;
004import androidx.room.Dao;
005import androidx.room.Delete;
006import androidx.room.Insert;
007import androidx.room.Query;
008import androidx.room.Update;
009import edu.cnm.deepdive.appstarter.model.entity.Preset;
010import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Completable;
011import io.reactivex.rxjava3.core.Single;
012import io.reactivex.rxjava3.disposables.CompositeDisposable;
013import java.util.List;
014@Dao
015public interface PresetDao {
016  @Insert
017  Single<Long> insert(Preset preset);
018
019  @Update
020  Single<Integer> update(Preset preset);
021
022  @Delete
023 Single<Integer> delete(Preset preset);
024
025  @Query("SELECT * FROM preset WHERE preset_id = :presetid")
026LiveData<Preset> select(Long presetid);
027  @Query("SELECT * FROM preset WHERE preset_name = :presetname")
028  LiveData<Preset> selectByName(String presetname);
029
030  @Query("SELECT * FROM preset ORDER BY preset_name ASC")
031  LiveData<List<Preset>> selectAllPresets();
032
033  @Query("SELECT * FROM preset WHERE user_id = :userid")
034LiveData<List<Preset>> selectUserPresets(Long userid);
035
036}
